{
  "stem": "7157.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But-- so that was some incidents you might say before the war when I was at the age of, say, zero to four.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He also liked to give us candy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He would line up-- in Europe they had these chocolate candies that are made like little figures.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And inside is some kind of a syrup, you know, like a raspberry or strawberry syrup.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he would line these up and my brother and I would go through a few of these.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So my memories are very, very pleasant at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My father's name, incidentally, was Meno or Menachim Mendel Geminder.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I have to at this point say, 'Guh-min-der.' Because actually the name was pronounced 'Guh-min-der' in Europe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When I came to this country, things were-- I wanted to make things easy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I didn't want to stand out the most, so you know how it is when you're a greenhorn.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I was advised to pronounce the name, 'Jeh-mine-der.' Later, of course, I found that many of my cousins living in this country, born in this country, pronounced the name 'Guh-min-der,' the way it should be pronounced.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we still go by 'Jeh-mine-der.' So that was my father's name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my mother's name is Bertha.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she went by the name of Bertl, B-E-R-T-L.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she-- she had-- my grandfathers from my father's side were already dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But my grandparents from my mother's side were alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were in the-- on the scene, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so was my mother's brother, an older brother by name of Artur.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Glotzer.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The name was Glotzer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my grandfather's name was Ira Glotzer, and my mother's name was Glotzer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, an interesting story-- of course, I was told this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wasn't born yet-- of how my parents met.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
